{"tid":1889560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【TWITTER 暗藏 YOUTUBE 戰線？！？！】跟進黃標事件！","createTime":"2020-02-20T16:37:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T07:01:41.000Z","uid":43936,"like":71,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"baa55a6df87f48580b76efec747dc726411f872f","tid":1889560,"uid":43936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T16:37:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望大家有持續每日twitter嘅好習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴晚有手足tweet咗關於黃絲武漢肺炎videos被demonetized（黃標）<br />\n之後YouTube有應，不過只係敷衍了事嘅回應<br />\n主要話武漢肺炎係敏感topic<br />\n<br />\n之後都手足有質問YouTube點解藍絲嘅片會冇事<br />\n亦都有好多手足加入質問YouTube<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d9z9u0d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd9z9u0d.png&h=ca146770&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FPTFBGS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFPTFBGS.png&h=6247c859&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家想大家一齊幫手<br />\n將依件事再推大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原tweet: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/fight4hongkong/status/1230143481491816448?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffight4hongkong%2Fstatus%2F1230143481491816448%3Fs%3D21&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqFy8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=ab9601bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffight4hongkong%2Fstatus%2F1230143481491816448%3Fs%3D21&h=6c7f8c76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/fight4hongkong/status/1230143481491816448?s=21</a><br />\nYouTube 回應: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/fight4hongkong/status/1230143481491816448?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u